Investor Education
Domini Impact Investments offers a family of mutual funds to help you meet your financial goals. You may invest in our funds through a variety of account types designed to address the range of investment objectives you may have, whether you are seeking to provide for your retirement, finance a child’s education or simply to build wealth.
Whether you are a novice or experienced investor, this section of our website is designed to provide you with the information you need to get started, and to manage your investments as you come closer to your goals.
Mutual fund basics
Retirement planning 
Saving for your child’s college education.
Basics of Responsible Investing, a strategy that recognizes that our investment decisions have an impact, every day.
Learn more about why Domini might be the right choice for you. If you prefer to speak with a Domini representative in person, please contact us today. 



